Theremon looked shocked. 'You mean they refused to come in out of the open? Where'd they sleep?'\par
'In the open.'\par
'They should have forced them inside.'\par
'Oh, they did, they did. Whereupon these people went into violent hysterics and did their best to bat their brains out against the nearest wall. Once you got them inside, you couldn't keep them there without a strait jacket or a heavy dose of tranquilizer.'\par
