Sheerin spoke, and it was with an effort that he made it sound matter-of-fact. 'I think I heard Yimot's voice. He and Faro are probably back. Let's go in and see what kept them.'\par
'Might as well!' muttered Theremon. He drew a long breath and seemed to shake himself. The tension was broken.\par
